@startuml activity-fanout
' The controller's activity fan-out: the 15s per-namespace cache, the per-Pod-IP par fan-out, the merge, and the filter.
' Source of truth: docs/src/gateways/user/activation-and-activity.md
!include _style.puml

participant "AgentReconciler" as rec #87CEEB
participant "15s per-namespace\ncache (reconciler-local)" as cache #F5F5F5
participant "Gateway\nPod A" as gwA #90EE90
participant "Gateway\nPod B" as gwB #90EE90
participant "Gateway\nPod C" as gwC #F5F5F5

rec -> cache : activity for namespace X?

alt #FFF8DC cache hit (inside the 15s window)
  cache --> rec : per-agent timestamps, both sources
  note over rec, cache
    **Zero HTTP.** Every other agent reconcile
    in namespace X within the window reads from here.
  end note

else cache miss or window expired
  par #F5F5F5 fan-out, one call per gateway Pod IP
    rec -> gwA : GET /v1/activity?namespace=X
    gwA --> rec : {replicaStartedAt,\n agents{gatewayTraffic, heartbeat}}
  else
    rec -> gwB : GET /v1/activity?namespace=X
    gwB --> rec : {replicaStartedAt, agents{...}}
  else
    rec ->x gwC : GET /v1/activity?namespace=X
    note over gwC
      Unreachable (connection refused
      or timeout): **skipped**. Data from
      the remaining replicas is used.
    end note
  end

  note over rec, gwC #FFE4B5
    Dialed **by Pod IP, not the Service**.
    The Service round-robins, so it would return
    a single replica's partial view.
    ....
    Pod IPs are not in the gateway cert's SAN, so the
    transport pins tls.Config.ServerName to the gateway
    Service DNS. SAN verification still passes, and the
    chain is still checked against agentry-ca.
  end note

  rec -> rec : merge: **most recent timestamp**\n**per agent, per source**
  rec -> cache : store for 15s
end

rec -> rec : **then** apply the activitySource filter:\ngatewayTraffic | heartbeat | max of both

note over rec
  The filter runs **after** the merge, and the controller owns it.
  The gateway always returns both sources and never reads Agent specs.
end note

legend bottom
  The cache is why this is affordable: it turns **O(agents x replicas)**
  HTTP calls per window into **O(namespaces x replicas)**.
endlegend
@enduml
